install dependecy:
1 redis
  http://redis.io/
2 python redis, sudo easy_install redis
  http://pypi.python.org/pypi/redis/
3 mongo
  http://www.mongodb.org/
4 pymongo, easy_install pymongo
  http://api.mongodb.org/python/current/
5 scrapy
  http://scrapy.org/
6 thrift, pythrift
  http://thrift.apache.org/
7 gocr
  http://jocr.sourceforge.net/
8 PIL, sudo easy_install PIL
  http://www.pythonware.com/products/pil/
9 google-chartwrapper, sudo easy_install -U GChartWrapper
  http://code.google.com/p/google-chartwrapper/
  http://www.haijd.net/archive/computer/google/google_chart_api/api.html

当我编译好程序后，想进入gdb调试程序，然后出现下面错误信息：
gdb: error while loading shared libraries: libexpat.so.1: cannot open shared
object file: No such file or directory

在网上搜了很长时间找到解决方法，其实方法很简单，就是建立一个软链接：
ln -s /usr/lib/libexpat.so /usr/lib/libexpat.so.1

这是因为在/usr/lib里找不到libexpat.so.1，但在/usr/lib里有libexpat.so，这样就可以通过软链接找到这个库。
